 Hydras had a 3d map of the world come up over the table. "The maximals and 
the tripred have formed an alliance it seems..or they are trying to. 4 of my 
old minions have joined them as well...but they are of no worry to me. What I 
worry about is the Maximals. If you found it wiser we could attack the 
maximal base first catching them off guard trying to strike down the head 
before it has a chance to regroup...thought the tripred base would be for 
susceptible to an attack."

--part1_90.2dac0de7.2ae427ba_boundary
